'''Rett syndrome''' is an almost entirely [[female]] based disorder which affects [[girl]]s. This condition is a neurological disorder which involves the [[brain]]'s grey matter. The clinical features include small [[hand]]s and [[feet]]. People with Rett syndrome also have [[mental retardation]] and [[scoliosis]].

